---
title: Steelhead Trout & Sweet Potato Risotto with Creamy Grape Sauce
description: When in doubt, go for trout. That’s our motto anyway, and it’ll be yours too once you try it over this cheesy sweet potato risotto! While the risotto simmers to a dreamy texture, you’ll sear the garlic powder seasoned trout until flaky and delicate, then start a creamy grape sauce that rounds the dish with sweetness and vinegary tang. Everything’s garnished with thyme for a colorful and richly flavored dish that’s sure to make your every fish wish come true!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steelhead-trout-sweet-potato-risotto-a0b64da0.jpg
